	moment) support. Other minor changes.

2008-06-07  Filippo Argiolas <filippo dot argiolas at gmail dot com>
	* gst-libs/gst/gl/gstglshader.c:
	* gst-libs/gst/gl/gstglshader.h:
	* gst-libs/gst/gl/gstglprogram.h:
	Merged first work for Google Summer of Code 2008.
	Initial draft for a couple of GObject classes to manage GLSL Program
	and Shader Objects. It's far from complete but usable yet, still need
	some data structure to track which shader are attached with which
	programs, uniform variables support etc
